{"type": "article", "id": 20560, "title": "圆环衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-12T07:13:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135105oaYQzfhtAxq3C5HF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组衣架是圆环结构，细看时可以发现衣架表面微妙的旋转。乌克兰的设计师 Viktor Puzur 从回收的圆筒纸板上斜向切割，形成了这些圆环，在上面钻孔安装金属挂钩后做成一个衣架。衣架有一个流动的弧度，可以直接悬挂围巾或首饰，与饰品相互搭配，一起成为装饰。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135103wfZPg5oAUsx8TvqC.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135103UDqnp6sJQP1XOF7g.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"345\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.43125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135104JWCmciAknTD8VPYp.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135104nDg2RI1iWGwtfL6m.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1077\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.34625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}